SAMLProcessingCapturingFilter - Class in cat.gencat.ctti.canigo.arch.security.saml.authentication.filter
Extends Spring Security SAML processing filter for the Assertion Consumer Service (or webSSO in Springspeak) in order to: Extract the assertion in its base64 form and keep it in the HTTP session, so that it can later be retrieved and exchanged for a JWT token. Validate the assertion signature.
